              I've been lucky enough to work on products from the initial "what if we..." moment all the way through 
              to launch, using my technical background to bridge the gap between business goals and what's actually 
              possible to build.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
              I'm all about making smart decisions based on data and real user feedback, not just gut feelings. 
              I've helped companies make some serious revenue through solid product strategies, and I've pitched 
              business cases to some pretty senior folks at Fortune 500 companies.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
              As a disability advocate and wheelchair user myself, I'm passionate about making sure digital products work for everyone. 
              I bring accessibility into every product decision because I believe everyone deserves amazing 
              digital experiences because equity matters. Always.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <Image 
            src={headshotImage} 
            alt="Camilo Pires - Product Manager and App Developer" 
            width={512}
            height={512}
            class="w-64 h-64 object-cover rounded-full shadow-lg mb-6"
            loading="eager"
            sizes="(max-width: 768px) 256px, 512px"
            quality={95}
            format="webp"
          />
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-8 w-full">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6">Core Values</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
