          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Conference presentations</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Accessibility advocacy talks</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Technical workshops</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Industry panel discussions</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Educational seminars</li>
